{"tid":153270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手］今日生日，屋企人求其留咗件蛋糕畀我","createTime":"2017-03-12T12:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T13:02:18.000Z","uid":39614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0853545505addcc808aa4de6be0d68424384ecff","tid":153270,"uid":39614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"今日家姐打電話畀我話買蛋糕同我慶祝生日，我就好期待今晚有得食蛋糕啦，點知返到屋企，老母話留咗件蛋糕畀我喺雪櫃<br />\n我開嚟睇，佢用個湯盒裝住，成件蛋糕仲返轉咗<br />\n家姐仲要sd佢個仔唱生日歌同幫我吹蠟燭嘅片上屋企個大group，而我因為唔用wechat而唔喺個group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講我仲以為係佢個仔生日，好心留件蛋糕畀我食，真係多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grTm4DB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrTm4DB.jpg&h=4be5576b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個蛋糕原本係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egX2G8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegX2G8D.jpg&h=2069e5b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5c1d48649cb7e614606095b2e5fe4b42fccdeed","tid":153270,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"好唔重視你, SOSAD"},{"pid":"3d979ccd7940b14314c6abe210e7986eee414e4f","tid":153270,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2015-07/31/11/enhanced/webdr03/anigif_enhanced-1568-1438356601-5_preview.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.buzzfeed.com%2Fbuzzfeed-static%2Fstatic%2F2015-07%2F31%2F11%2Fenhanced%2Fwebdr03%2Fanigif_enhanced-1568-1438356601-5_preview.gif&h=0a6ebf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb5d85e3235240f5015c00aa1b8c3ecc2b00526","tid":153270,"uid":89729,